OL,3,CMeet the bookbinder with a key role in
OL,4,Cthe Booker Prize ceremony
OL,6,FKate has taken on the challenge and is
OL,7,Fnow due to head to the ceremony this
OL,8,Fevening to give the one-off copy of
OL,9,FJames to its author Percival Everett,
OL,10,Fwho is favourite to win this year's
OL,11,Fprize.
OL,13,FThe book is a re-telling of Mark
OL,14,FTwain's Adventures of Huckleberry
OL,15,FFinn, told from the viewpoint of
OL,16,Fescaped slave 'Jim'. It is the
OL,17,Ffavourite to win this year's Booker
OL,18,FPrize.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
