OL,3,CMeet the bookbinder with a key role in
OL,4,Cthe Booker Prize ceremony
OL,6,FKate has spent 150 hours on the
OL,7,Fbinding - including reading the book,
OL,8,Fresearching it, coming up with the
OL,9,Fdesign and creating it.
OL,11,F"It's very much the artistic response
OL,12,Fto the text," she told ITV News.
OL,14,F"We read the book, we research around
OL,15,Fit, we try to come up with a design
OL,16,Fwhich reflects the story. It's not
OL,17,Fjust the cover design for a book
OL,18,Fjacket, it's the whole book, inside,
OL,19,Foutside, all the way around.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
