OL,3,CMeet the bookbinder with a key role in
OL,4,Cthe Booker Prize ceremony
OL,6,F"Then they get presented to the author
OL,7,Fat the ceremony.
OL,9,F"We get to sit at the table with the
OL,10,Fauthor and go to the champagne
OL,11,Freception. It's the most glamorous
OL,12,Fpart of my job".
OL,14,FIt's the fifth time Kate has been
OL,15,Fasked to take part in the Booker Prize
OL,16,Fevent. Kate also worked on Percival
OL,17,FEverett's novel 'The Trees' which was
OL,18,Fshortlisted in 2022.
OL,20,FShe admits the subject matter for
OL,21,F'James' was "difficult".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
