OL,3,CMeet the bookbinder with a key role in
OL,4,Cthe Booker Prize ceremony
OL,6,F"It's very much the slave's experience
OL,7,Fof the Deep South," she said. "There's
OL,8,Fa lot of anger running through it.
OL,9,FPercival Everett is telling a very
OL,10,Fserious story but with a sense of
OL,11,Fhumour."
OL,13,FSpeaking about her design, she said:
OL,14,F"I had to reign in my initial response
OL,15,Fwhich was all about the whipping and
OL,16,Fscarring, the blood and the anger, but
OL,17,FI thought that wouldn't be respectful
OL,18,Ffor the people who've been through
OL,19,Fthat.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
