OL,3,CMeet the bookbinder with a key role in
OL,4,Cthe Booker Prize ceremony
OL,6,FKate - who teaches bookbinding at Bath
OL,7,FSpa University - said she's looking
OL,8,Fforward to putting on her cocktail
OL,9,Fdress for the ceremony in London.
OL,11,F"It's a nice opportunity to get out
OL,12,Finto the real world, away from the
OL,13,Fslightly closeted world of
OL,14,Fbookbinding."
OL,16,FThe Booker Prize 2024 shortlist
